      "side": 1,
      "message": "I feel like we shouldn\u0027t worry about what the OP needs inside this setupDstRead function. Like once we are in this function we already know the op needs to read the dst. At this point all we care about is if the OpsTask itself is rendering to an MSAA target or not. And that should have all been setup before setupDstRead is called.",
