      "message": "\u003e At this point all we care about is if the OpsTask itself is rendering to an MSAA target or not.\n\nI think that\u0027s what op.usesMSAA() answers, right? It, together with opsTask-\u003eusesMSAASurface(), tells us whether the opsTask will need MSAA after adding this op.\n\n\u003e And that should have all been setup before setupDstRead is called.\n\nIt actually doesn\u0027t. The opsTask won\u0027t update itself to require MSAA until after we call addDrawOp, which happens after setupDstProxyView.",
